title: Wake Me Up When September Trends 8/31: Cam Newton, Ben Simmons, Caldor Fire, Premier League, Elizabeth Holmes, Paul Ryan, Madison Cawthorn
itunes:title: Wake Me Up When September Trends 8/31: Cam Newton, Ben Simmons, Caldor Fire, Premier League, Elizabeth Holmes, Paul Ryan, Madison Cawthorn
description:
In this edition of Wake Me Up When September Trends, Jack and Miles discuss Cam Newton getting cut from the Patriots, Ben Simmons refusing to return to the 76ers, the Caldor fire, Premier League transfers, Elizabeth Holmes' trial, Paul Ryan saying true statements?, and Madison Cawthorn really hoping we don't have to Civil War
